This is beautiful typer.

You may text your friend in telegram spelling words by one single letter
with 0.1s or 0.5s or 99s or whatever delay. Just like in INSTA stories.

To run this program just
1) Download letter_speller.py file
2) Make sure you got or your virtual enviroment got libraries
   mentiond in requirements.txt file.
3) Run the letter_speller.py
   (first time you have to log in your account from which you will text people)
4) Noway, bro, really please DO NOT steal my id&hash for api since I don't know
   where is the most suitable place to keep them. 

